    "created_at": "2014-10-11T22:18:58Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-10-11T22:18:58Z",
    "body": "If recursion _was_ possible with the old closure implementation, it would be a soundness bug. It is possible with the new closures but it takes some effort. A comparison to a VM language that's looking up the variables dynamically isn't really meaningful. I don't think there's an actionable issue here.\n",
