    "created_at": "2014-10-24T00:27:05Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-10-24T00:27:05Z",
    "body": "I just ran into this problem.  There is nothing wrong with wanting to use a recursive closure, if you need a recursive function that uses context from inside another function.  It shouldn't be necessary to use hacks to achieve this.\n",
