    "created_at": "2014-10-24T01:50:56Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-10-24T01:50:56Z",
    "body": "@comex: Recursion under the old closure scheme implies breaking the aliasing rules for `&mut T`. It is possible with the new closures but the syntax / semantics for those is still being ironed out. To get the same semantics as Python closures, you need to combine `Rc`, `Option` and `RefCell`.\n",
